\p
\v 3 Babusisiwe\x + Luka 6.20-23.\x* abayanga emoyeni\x + Hlab. 34.18.\x*; ngoba umbuso wamazulu ungowabo\x + 11.5. Jak. 2.5.\x*.
\v 4 Babusisiwe abalilayo\x + Isa. 57.18; 61.2,3. Joha. 16.20. Isam. 7.17; 21.4.\x*; ngoba bona bazaduduzwa.
\v 5 Babusisiwe abamnene; ngoba bona bazakudla ilifa lomhlaba\x + Hlab. 37.11.\x*.
\v 6 Babusisiwe abalambela labomela ukulunga; ngoba bona bazasuthiswa\x + Isa. 55.1. 65.13.\x*.
\v 7 Babusisiwe abalesihawu; ngoba bona bazahawukelwa\x + Hlab. 41.1. Zaga 14.21. 2 Tim. 1.16. Heb. 6.10.\x*.
\v 8 Babusisiwe abamhlophe enhliziyweni\x + Hlab. 24.4.\x*; ngoba bona bazabona uNkulunkulu\x + Heb. 12.14. 1 Joha. 3.2,3.\x*.
\v 9 Babusisiwe abalamulayo; ngoba bona bazathiwa ngabantwana bakaNkulunkulu.
\v 10 Babusisiwe abazingelwayo ngenxa yokulunga; ngoba umbuso wamazulu ungowabo\x + Roma 8.17. 2 Kor. 1.7; 4.17. 2 Tim. 2.12. 1 Pet. 2.19; 3.14; 4.13.14.\x*.
\v 11 Lina libusisiwe, nxa belithuka be\add li\add*zingela, bekhuluma okubi konke bemelana lani beqamba amanga, ngenxa yami;
\v 12 thokozani lithabe kakhulu, ngoba umvuzo wenu mkhulu emazulwini\x + Seb. 5.41. Roma 5.3. 2 Kor. 7.4; 12.10. Kol. 1.24. Heb. 10.34. Jak. 1.2.\x*; ngoba ngokunjalo babazingela abaprofethi abalandulelayo\x + 2 Lan. 36.16. Mat. 23.34,37. Luka 13.33,34. 1 Thes. 2.15. Neh. 9.26.\x*.
\s Itshwayi lokukhanya emhlabeni
\p
\v 13 Lina lilitshwayi lomhlaba; kodwa uba itshwayi seliduma lizatshwaywa ngani? Kalisasizi lutho, ngaphandle kokulahlwa phandle beselinyathelwa ngabantu\x + Mark. 9.50. Luka 14.34,35.\x*.
\v 14 Lina liyikukhanya komhlaba\x + Fil. 2.15. Zaga 4.18.\x*; umuzi omiswe phezu kwentaba ungesitheke;
\v 15 njalo kabalumathisi isibane\x + Mark. 4.21. Luka 8.16; 11.33.\x* basibeke ngaphansi kwesitsha, kodwa phezu kwesiqobane sesibane, besesibakhanyisela bonke abasendlini.
\v 16 Ngokunjalo kakukhanye ukukhanya kwenu phambi kwabantu, ukuze babone imisebenzi yenu emihle\x + 1 Pet. 2.12.\x*, badumise uYihlo osemazulwini\x + Joha. 15.8. Fil. 1.11. 1 Kor. 14.25.\x*.
\s Umlayo omdala lomlayo kaJesu Kristu
\p
\v 17 Lingacabangi ukuthi ngize ukuchitha umlayo kumbe abaprofethi\x + Roma 3.31. Roma 10.4. Gal. 3.24.\x*; angizanga ukuchitha kodwa ukugcwalisa.
\v 18 Ngoba ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kuze kudlule izulu lomhlaba, kakusoze kudlule ibadlana libe linye kumbe ichatshana libe linye emlayweni kuze kwenzeke konke\x + Luka 16.17. Isa. 40.8. 1 Pet. 1.25. Mat. 24.35.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho owephula owodwa kulimilayo emincinyane, afundise abantu ngokunjalo, uzathiwa ngomncinyane embusweni wamazulu; kodwa oyenzayo ayifundise, lowo uzathiwa mkhulu embusweni wamazulu\x + Jak. 2.10. Gal. 3.10.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba ngithi kini: Ngaphandle kokuthi ukulunga kwenu kwedlule okwababhali lokwabaFarisi\x + Roma 9.31; 10.3.\x*, kalisoze lingene embusweni wamazulu.
