\v 21 Lizwile ukuthi kwathiwa kwabasendulo: Ungabulali; laloba ngubani obulalayo, uzakuba lecala lokugwetshwa\x + Eks. 20.13. Dute. 5.17.\x*;
\v 22 kodwa mina ngithi kini: Wonke othukuthelela umfowabo kungelasizatho uzakuba lecala lokugwetshwa\x + 1 Joha. 3.15.\x*; lotshoyo kumfowabo \add ukuthi\add*: Siphukuphukundini! uzakuba lecala emphakathini\x + 10.17; 26.59. Mark. 13.9; 14.55; 15.1. Luka 22.66. Joha. 11.47. Seb. 4.15; 5.21,27,34,41; 6.12,15; 22.30; 23.1,6,15,20,28; 24.20.\x*; lotshoyo ukuthi: Sithuthandini\x + 7.26; 23.17,19; 25.2,3,8.\x*! uzakuba lecala lokusiwa esihogweni somlilo\x + 5.29,30.10.28; 18.9; 23.15,33. Mark. 9.43,45,47. Luka 12.5. Jak. 3.6.\x*.
\v 23 Ngakho uba uletha umnikelo wakho elathini\x + 8.4; 23.19.\x*, ubusukhumbula ulapho ukuthi umfowenu ulolutho olumelana lawe,
\v 24 tshiya lapho umnikelo wakho phambi kwelathi, uhambe, uqale ubuyisane lomfowenu, ubusuzonikela umnikelo wakho.
\v 25 Phangisa uzwane laye omangalelane lawe\x + Luka 12.58,59. Zaga 25.8.\x* usesendleleni laye\x + Hlab. 32.6. Isa. 55.6.\x*, hlezi omangalelane lawe akunikele kumahluleli, futhi umahluleli akunikele epholiseni\x + 26.58.\x*, ubusuphoselwa entolongweni.
\v 26 Ngiqinisile ngithi kuwe: Kawusoze uphume khona, uze ubhadale indibilitshi yokucina.
\p
\v 27 Lizwile ukuthi kwathiwa kwabasendulo\x + 5.21.\x*: Ungafebi\x + Eks. 20.14. Dute. 5.18.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa mina ngithi kini: Wonke okhangela owesifazana ukumkhanuka usefebile laye enhliziyweni yakhe\x + Jobe 31.1. Zaga 6.25. Gen. 34.2. 2 Sam. 11.2.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo uba ilihlo lakho lokunene likukhubekisa\x + 18.9. Mark. 9.47. Jobe 31.7.\x*, likhuphe u\add li\add*lahlele khatshana lawe\x + Dute. 13.6.19.12. Roma 8.13. 1 Kor. 9.27. Kol. 3.5.\x*; ngoba kungcono kuwe ukuthi kubhubhe sibe sinye sezitho zakho, lokuthi umzimba wakho wonke ungaphoselwa esihogweni\x + 5.29,30.10.28; 18.9; 23.15,33. Mark. 9.43,45,47. Luka 12.5. Jak. 3.6.\x*.
\v 30 Njalo uba isandla sakho sokunene sikukhubekisa, siqume u\add si\add*lahlele khatshana lawe\x + 18.8. Mark. 9.43.\x*; ngoba kungcono kuwe ukuthi kubhubhe sibe sinye sezitho zakho, lokuthi umzimba wakho wonke ungaphoselwa esihogweni\x + 5.29,30. 10.28; 18.9; 23.15,33. Mark. 9.43,45,47. Luka 12.5. Jak. 3.6.\x*.
\v 31 Kwathiwa-ke: Loba ngubani owala umkakhe, kumele amnike incwadi yesehlukaniso\x + Dute. 24.1. Jer. 3.1.\x*;
\v 32 kodwa mina ngithi kini: Loba ngubani owala umkakhe, ngaphandle kodaba lokufeba, umenza afebe, njalo loba ngubani omthathayo owaliweyo uyafeba.
\p
\v 33 Lizwile futhi ukuthi kwathiwa kwabasendulo\x + 5.21.\x*: Ungafungi amanga\x + Levi 19.12. Eks. 20.7. Nani 30.2. Dute. 5.11.\x*, kodwa gcwalisa izifungo zakho eNkosini\x + Dute. 23.23. Levi 5.4.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa mina ngithi kini: Lingafungi lakanye\x + Jak. 5.12. Mat. 23.16-18.\x*; loba ngezulu, ngoba liyisihlalo sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu\x + 5.23.22. Hlab. 11.4.\x*;
\v 35 loba ngomhlaba, ngoba uyisenabelo senyawo zakhe\x + 1 Lan. 28.2.\x*; loba ngeJerusalema, ngoba ingumuzi weNkosi enkulu\x + Hlab. 48.2. Hlab. 87.3.\x*;
\v 36 njalo ungafungi ngekhanda lakho, ngoba ungelwenze unwele lalunye lube mhlophe kumbe lube mnyama.
\v 37 Kodwa ilizwi lenu kalibe ngelokuthi: Yebo, yebo; hatshi, hatshi. Okudlula lokhu-ke kuvela komubi\x + Kol. 4.6. Mat. 5.33.\x*.
