\v 39 kodwa mina ngithi kini\x + Luka 6.29,30.\x*: Lingamelani lobubi\x + Zaga 20.22; 24.29. Roma 12.17. 1 Kor. 6.7. 1 Thes. 5.15. 1 Pet. 3.9. Dute. 32.35.\x*; kodwa loba ngubani\x + Isa. 50.6. 1 Kho. 22.24.\x* okuwakala esihlathini sokunene, mphendulele lesinye\x + 26.67.\x*;
\v 40 lalowo ofuna ukukumangalela lokuthatha isigqoko sakho, mtshiyele lesembatho;
\v 41 laloba ngubani okubamba ngamandla ukuthi uhambe imayili libe linye\x + 27.32. Mark. 15.21.\x*, hamba laye abe mabili.
\v 42 Mnike ocela kuwe\x + Hlab. 112.9. Zaga 21.26.\x*; njalo ungamfulatheli ofisa ukweboleka kuwe\x + Dute. 15.8,10. Hlab. 37.26; 112.5. Luka 6.34,35.\x*.
