\v 43 Lizwile ukuthi kwathiwa: Wothanda umakhelwane wakho\x + Levi 19.18.\x*, njalo uzonde isitha sakho\x + Dute. 23.6.\x*;
\v 44 kodwa mina ngithi kini: Thandani izitha zenu, libabusise abaliqalekisayo, libaphathe kuhle abalizondayo\x + Luka 6.27,28,35. Roma 12.14,20. Eks. 23.4. Jobe 31.29,30. Zaga 24.17; 25.21.\x*, libakhulekele abaliphatha kubi, labalizingelayo\x + Luka 23.34. Seb. 7.60. 1 Kor. 4.12,13. 1 Pet. 2.23; 3.9.\x*;
